info.+content: ヒーリングっど♥プリキュア

Nodoka Hanadera encounters a magical "healing animal" named Rabirin, sent from the Healing Garden, a world which protects the earth and has been attacked by the Byogens, who seek to spread disease and destroy the earth. With Rabirin's help, Nodoka becomes a Pretty Cure and alongside her friends and their Healing Animal companions, fights to protect the earth from the Byogens.
ヒーリングっど♥プリキュア | 東映アニメーション
